{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-151","title":"害怕恐惧","sectionId":"chapter-07","sectionTitle":"喜怒哀乐听你说","pageStart":762,"pageEnd":765,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":14,"duplicateEntryCount":14,"pages":[{"number":762,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"151 害怕恐惧"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"fear [fɪə(r)]","headword":"fear"},{"type":"definition","text":"n./v.恐惧，害怕（宾语是害怕的根源）"},{"type":"note","text":"◎for fear of为了避免/in fear害怕"},{"type":"entry","text":"horror [ˈhɒrə(r)]","headword":"horror"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.恐怖，战栗"},{"type":"note","text":"◎horror story恐怖故事"},{"type":"entry","text":"terror [ˈterə(r)]","headword":"terror"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.恐怖；可怕的人（事）"},{"type":"note","text":"◎in terror恐惧地"}]},{"number":763,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"shaking [ˈʃeɪkɪŋ]","headword":"shaking"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.颤抖"},{"type":"entry","text":"frightened [ˈfraɪtnd]","headword":"frightened"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.受惊吓的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎get frightened受惊吓，感到害怕"},{"type":"entry","text":"scary [ˈskeəri]","headword":"scary"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.引起恐慌的"},{"type":"entry","text":"fearful [ˈfɪəfl]","headword":"fearful"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.可怕的；不安的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎fearful consequences可怕的后果"}]},{"number":764,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"trembling [ˈtrembl]","headword":"trembling"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.发抖的"},{"type":"entry","text":"horribly [ˈhɒrəbli]","headword":"horribly"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad. 可怕地"},{"type":"entry","text":"freak out 崩溃","headword":"freak out"}]},{"number":765,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"be scared to death 吓得要死","headword":"be scared to death"},{"type":"entry","text":"jump out of my skin 吓死了","headword":"jump out of my skin"},{"type":"entry","text":"on pins and needles 头皮发麻","headword":"on pins and needles"},{"type":"entry","text":"set one's teeth on edge 害怕得要死","headword":"set one's teeth on edge"},{"type":"text","text":"be afraid to do sth. 害怕做某事"},{"type":"text","text":"intimidate sb. by 以…恐吓某人"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：At the sight of blood he drew back in horror. （他一看到血就惊"},{"type":"text","text":"恐地连忙后退。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：He was such a coward. （他真是个胆小鬼。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：She was relieved of dread. （她的恐惧心理消除了。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Good for her. （太好了。）"}]}]}